rows.label: tlk70000070_01_msg0002
rows.name:
What's that? You want to know how
to get to the desert?

rows.label: tlk70000070_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Head out from here in the opposite
direction to Olnard's Trail. You should
pass through the Braying Canyon.

rows.label: tlk70000070_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Come out of the canyon and the
Dannagh Desert's right there.

rows.label: tlk70000070_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, good luck. I know it's not such
a happening place, but come visit us
every once in a while. For me.
